兩樣。」<br />\n<br />\n學生 Siani Zuniga：「當我聽說社會主義時，這充滿著貧窮，他們（想）在美國實施，（他們認為）社會主義讓生活變好。但這根本不會，那邊的共產主義國家，錢沒有價值，基本上錢被扔掉了。」<br />\n<br />\n他們表示，在越共、中共等政權下生活過的人都會知道，共產主義將為人類帶來毀滅性的災難。因此，美國人民將堅定捍衛人權與自由。<br />\n<br />\n目前，加州各地仍持續在進行罷免紐森的連署行動，活動預計於今年3月10日截止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20210113/video/287174.html?反對極左洗腦教育%20加州民眾罷免州長紐森\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20210113%2Fvideo%2F287174.html%3F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%A5%B5%E5%B7%A6%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%2520%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%9E%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%BD%B7%E5%85%8D%E5%B7%9E%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%90%E6%A3%AE&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU34fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=dc65f14a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20210113/video/287174.html?反對極左洗腦教育%20加州民眾罷免州長紐森</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"big tech 快d和諧依班人啦"},{"pid":"e8e65e9da244ce25cc0eab542ca81d919ea12407","tid":2383898,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4aeb646d3169c98fa5e32e60bdddcb3c983795","tid":2383898,"uid":303554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"性教育真係要好小心咁教 太早教就會導致大量墮胎 完全避談就好似華人社會咁 又係會出事"},{"pid":"41e422934134d4e777da1c68d8d5103c01f4ecb0","tid":2383898,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"又關連登仔事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}